A mistake by White - now Black can level the game. 24.Rxd5 cxd5 25. Bb6 and White captures the a pawn - I think this should give white a convincing advantage due to the nature of the passed pawn on the Queenside. Black can't even capture at Bxh2 because White plays g3 and traps the bishop.
